name: INMediaUserContext.SubscriptionStatus
desc: Constants that describe the current description status.

items.name: case unknown
items.desc: A code that indicates the app doesn’t offer subscriptions or the subscription status is unavailable.

items.name: case notSubscribed
items.desc: A code that indicates the user isn’t a subscriber, but subscriptions are available.

items.name: case subscribed
items.desc: A code that indicates the user currently has a subscription.
